{
  "texts": [
    "The task of temporal action detection in a completely unsupervised environment is called action co-localization (ACL).",
    "Only the total number of unique actions occurring in the video dataset is known.",
    "Very few studies have attempted this method so far.",
    "Gong et al. (. 2020a) made the first attempt to explore this problem in an unsupervised environment.",
    "In order to solve ACL, they proposed a two-step \"clustering + localization\" iterative process."
  ]
}